  QuestName: Washed Up
  LevelRequirment: 0
  Instructions: You wash up on a beach and you're already on your feet? Ha! I can
    tell just by looking at you.. you're a fighter! Here, take this. It's not much,
    but let's see what you can do with it. There are <color=orange>training dummies</color>
    to the <color=green>east</color>. Go show me your swing!
  Deliver: I knew it! I knew the moment I saw you. You're exactly what this island
    needs. Rest for a moment, I need to think about what comes next.
